text: Paula Winslowe was an American voice actress. She voices Bambi's Mother from Bambi (1942) and Princess Esmeralda from A Knight for a Day (1946) on Disney and Jane Jetson from The Jetsons (1962-1989) on Hanna Barbera. Category:1910 births Category:1996 deaths Category:American voice actors
title: Paula Winslowe
